ESR is <a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/esr-expands-its-qi2-25w-wireless-charging-lineup-advancing-everyday-charging-at-ces-2026-302653572.html">updating its line of CryoBoost chargers</a>, adding new Qi2.2 options that can charge an <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/iphone-17/">iPhone 17</a> at up to 25W. CryoBoost is ESR's feature that uses active cooling to improve wireless charging speeds.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2026/01/esr-qi2-25w-chargers.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1125" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1031542" /><br/>
The &#36;90 <a href="https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0FHQDKX7G">CryoBoost Foldable 3-in-1 Magnetic Charging Station</a> has a compact design that's ideal for travel. It folds down to 15.8mm, but can charge an <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/iphone/">iPhone</a> at up to 25W, an Apple Watch, and AirPods at the same time.<br/>
<br/>
The &#36;100 <a href="https://www.esrtech.com/products/3-in-1-25w-qi2-2-wireless-charging-station-us-plug-black">CryoBoost 3-in-1 Magnetic Charging Station</a> offers the same feature set as the foldable model, but in a design optimized for the desktop. It has a detachable Apple Watch charger, and the &zwnj;iPhone&zwnj; charging stand supports portrait and landscape modes. Sleep Mode turns off the light and the fan for quiet, LED-free charging.<br/>
<br/>
ESR says that its upcoming 10,000 mAh MagSlim Power Bank is the thinnest Qi2.2 25W power bank on the market, measuring in at 13.8mm thick. It too is able to charge the &zwnj;iPhone 17&zwnj; models at up to 25W, just like <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/magsafe/">MagSafe</a>.<br/>
<br/>
